title: Black Sheep 1996 DVDrip
description:
Here is the DVD Rip of Chris Farley and David Spade's hilarious 1996 Comedy: Black Sheep.

Don't forget to seed - especially for great movies like this one! :D

From the .txt file:

Plot Outline..:>Comedy about the prospective Washington State Governor Al Donnelly (Matheson) whose only stumbling block on the road to power is his embarrassing younger brother Mike (Farley). To keep him out of mischief, Al forces one of his aides, Steve Dodds (Spade) to keep an eye on him during the election. However, this is easier said than done..
